      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Everything you need to know about our telehealth platform</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid gap-6 md:gap-8 animate-fade-in-up" data-controller="faq" style="animation-delay: 0.2s">
      <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:border-medgemma-200 transition-all duration-300">
        <button class="w-full flex justify-between items-center text-left focus:outline-none group" 
                data-faq-target="question" 
                data-action="click->faq#toggle"
                aria-expanded="true">
          <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 group-hover:text-medgemma-600 transition-colors">Is MedGemma Health covered by insurance?</h3>
          <i class="fas fa-chevron-down text-medgemma-500 transform transition-transform duration-300" 
             data-faq-target="icon"></i>
        </button>
        <div class="mt-4 text-gray-600" data-faq-target="answer">
          <p>Yes, MedGemma Health works with most major insurance providers. During registration, you can enter your insurance details, and our system will verify your coverage. We also offer affordable self-pay options starting at just $49 per consultation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:border-medgemma-200 transition-all duration-300">
        <button class="w-full flex justify-between items-center text-left focus:outline-none group" 
                data-faq-target="question" 
                data-action="click->faq#toggle"
                aria-expanded="false">
          <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 group-hover:text-medgemma-600 transition-colors">What medical conditions can be treated through the platform?</h3>
          <i class="fas fa-chevron-down text-medgemma-500 transform transition-transform duration-300" 
             data-faq-target="icon"></i>
        </button>
        <div class="mt-4 text-gray-600 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300" data-faq-target="answer">
          <p>MedGemma Health can help diagnose and treat a wide range of non-emergency conditions, including:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>Skin conditions (rashes, acne, eczema)</li>
            <li>Cold and flu symptoms</li>
            <li>Allergies</li>
            <li>UTIs and other minor infections</li>
            <li>Prescription refills</li>
            <li>Mental health concerns</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-2">For emergencies or life-threatening conditions, please call 911 or go to your nearest emergency room.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:border-medgemma-200 transition-all duration-300">
        <button class="w-full flex justify-between items-center text-left focus:outline-none group" 
                data-faq-target="question" 
                data-action="click->faq#toggle"
                aria-expanded="false">
          <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 group-hover:text-medgemma-600 transition-colors">How accurate is the AI diagnosis?</h3>
          <i class="fas fa-chevron-down text-medgemma-500 transform transition-transform duration-300" 
             data-faq-target="icon"></i>
        </button>
        <div class="mt-4 text-gray-600 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300" data-faq-target="answer">
          <p>Our AI diagnostic system has been trained on millions of medical cases and achieves an accuracy rate of over 92% for common conditions. However, all AI diagnoses are verified by board-certified physicians before any treatment plan is provided, ensuring you receive the highest quality care.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- FAQ Item 4 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:border-medgemma-200 transition-all duration-300">
        <button class="w-full flex justify-between items-center text-left focus:outline-none group" 
                data-faq-target="question" 
                data-action="click->faq#toggle"
                aria-expanded="false">
          <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 group-hover:text-medgemma-600 transition-colors">Is my medical data secure?</h3>
          <i class="fas fa-chevron-down text-medgemma-500 transform transition-transform duration-300" 
             data-faq-target="icon"></i>
        </button>
        <div class="mt-4 text-gray-600 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300" data-faq-target="answer">
          <p>Absolutely. MedGemma Health is fully HIPAA compliant and uses end-to-end encryption for all data transmission. Your medical information is stored securely and is never shared with third parties without your explicit consent. We implement enterprise-grade security measures to protect your privacy.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- FAQ Item 5 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:border-medgemma-200 transition-all duration-300">
        <button class="w-full flex justify-between items-center text-left focus:outline-none group" 
                data-faq-target="question" 
                data-action="click->faq#toggle"
                aria-expanded="false">
          <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 group-hover:text-medgemma-600 transition-colors">How soon can I get a prescription?</h3>
          <i class="fas fa-chevron-down text-medgemma-500 transform transition-transform duration-300" 
             data-faq-target="icon"></i>
        </button>
        <div class="mt-4 text-gray-600 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300" data-faq-target="answer">
          <p>If a medication is part of your treatment plan, prescriptions can be issued immediately following your consultation. You can choose to have them sent electronically to your preferred pharmacy for pickup within hours, or have medications delivered directly to your door (typically 1-2 business days).</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="text-center mt-12 animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.4s">
      <a href="/faq" class="inline-flex items-center text-medgemma-600 font-medium hover:text-medgemma-700 transition-colors">
        View all FAQs
        <i class="fas fa-arrow-right ml-2"></i>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

